Masu goyon bayan sauya sunan, ciki har da Firayim Minista Zoran Zaev, sun yi jayayya cewa wannan farashi ne da ya dace a biya don samun izinin shiga cikin hukumomi kamar EU da NATO don Makidoniya, ɗaya daga cikin ƙasashen da aka haifa daga rushewar Yugoslavia.
"Na zo yau don in yi wa 'yan Macedonia muryata don nan gaba na ƙasar, don matasa su iya rayuwa cikin 'yanci a ƙarƙashin hadayar Tarayyar Turai domin hakan na nufin rayuwa mafi aminci ga dukanmu", in ji Olivera Georgijevska, mai shekara 79, a Skopje.
