Amurka za ta iya amfani da Rundunar Sojan Ruwa a matsayin "tashin kai" don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha - Sakataren Cikin Gida
"Idan ya cancanta" Washington na iya neman taimakon Navy don hana makamashin Rasha isa kasuwa, har da a Gabas ta Tsakiya, Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida na Amurka, Ryan Zinke ya bayyana, kamar yadda Washington Examiner ya ruwaito.
Zinke ya yi zaton cewa yadda Rasha ta yi amfani da wutar lantarki a Syria - musamman ma a wurin da take aiki a kan gayyatar gwamnati - ya zama hujja don bincika sabon kasuwar makamashi.
