Jakadan Amurka ya zargi kasar Sin da "karyar" ta hanyar "tallan talla"
Wata mako bayan da jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wata sanarwa mai shafuffuka hudu a wata jaridar Amurka da ke cewa amfanin cinikin Amurka da China na musayar juna, jakadan Amurka a kasar Sin ya zargi Beijing da amfani da jaridar Amurka wajen yada propaganda.
Shugaban Amurka Donald Trump a ranar Laraba ya yi magana da China Daily mai biyan kuɗi a cikin Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa - bayan ya zargi kasar Sin da ƙoƙarin shiga tsakani a zaben Amurka na ranar 6 ga Nuwamba, zargin da kasar Sin ta musanta.
