Masu kirkiro na yanar gizo na duniya suna shirin kaddamar da sabuwar intanet don fuskantar Google da Facebook
Tim Berners-Lee, wanda ya kirkiro yanar gizo ta duniya, ya kaddamar da wani kamfani wanda ke neman ya yi nasara da Facebook, Amazon, da Google.
Sabon aikin da wannan mashahurin masanin fasaha ya yi, Inrupt, wani kamfani ne da aka gina daga dandalin Berners-Lee na bude tushen, Solid.
Solid yana ba masu amfani damar zaɓar inda aka adana bayanan su da kuma wanda aka ba su damar samun damar yin amfani da duk wani bayani.
A wata hira ta musamman da aka yi da Fast Company, Berners-Lee ya yi ta yin dariya cewa manufar Inrupt ita ce "mulkin duniya".
"Dole ne mu fara yanzu", in ji ta daga kamfanin.
"Wannan lokaci ne na tarihi".
Wannan app yana amfani da fasahar Solid wadda ke ba mutane damar yin "keɓaɓɓen ajiyar bayanai ta kan layi" ko POD.
Wannan ajiyar tana iya ɗauke da jerin sunayen abokan aiki, jerin ayyuka, kalandar, ɗakin karatu, da kuma wasu kayan aiki na mutum da na sana'a.
Kamar Google Drive, Microsoft Outlook, Slack, da Spotify duk suna samuwa a cikin mai bincike guda ɗaya kuma duk a lokaci guda.
Abin da ke da ban sha'awa game da adana bayanan sirri a kan layi shi ne cewa ya dogara da mai amfani wanda zai iya samun dama ga wane irin bayani.
A cikin kamfanoni ana kiran shi "haɓaka mutum ta hanyar bayanai".
Manufar kafa Inrupt, a cewar Shugaba John Bruce, ita ce kamfanin ya ba da albarkatu, tsari, da kuma ƙwarewa don taimakawa wajen sa Solid ya kasance ga kowa.
A yanzu kamfanin ya kunshi Berners-Lee, Bruce, wani dandamali na tsaro da IBM ta sayi, wasu masu tasowa da aka yi wa aiki don yin aikin, da kuma ƙungiyar masu ba da kai na masu samar da lambar.
Tun daga wannan makon, masu bunkasa fasaha a duk faɗin duniya za su iya ƙirƙirar aikace-aikacen rarraba kansu ta amfani da kayan aikin da ke cikin gidan yanar gizon Inrupt.
Berners-Lee ya ce shi da tawagarsa ba su yi magana da "Facebook da Google ba game da ko za su gabatar da canji na gaba daya wanda za a juya duk tsarin kasuwancin su cikin dare.
"Ba mu nemi izinin su ba".
A wani rubutu da ya wallafa a Medium a ranar Asabar, Berners-Lee ya rubuta cewa "aikin Inrupt shi ne samar da makamashi da kuma tsarin halittu na kasuwanci domin taimakawa wajen kare mutuncin da ingancin sabon yanar gizo da aka gina a kan Solid".
A shekara ta 1994, Berners-Lee ya canja Intanet sa'ad da ya kafa Ƙungiyar Yanar Gizo ta Duniya a Cibiyar Fasaha ta Massachusetts.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya zama babbar murya a cikin tsaka tsaki na muhawara ta hanyar sadarwa.
Ko da a lokacin da aka kaddamar da Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance Founder da kuma Daraktan World Wide Web Consortium, Web Foundation, da kuma Open Data Institute.
"Ina da tabbaci sosai game da zamanin yanar gizo na gaba", in ji Berners-Lee.
