Mai wasan Olympics Tom Daley ya ce ya girma da rashin kunya saboda matsalar jima'i - amma hakan ya ba shi dalili ya yi nasara.
Mutumin mai shekara 24 ya ce bai san hakan ba har sai da ya shiga makarantar sakandare, cewa "ba kowa ba ne yake kama da ni".
A jawabinsa na farko a gidan rediyo na 4 Desert Island Discs wanda Lauren Laverne ta gabatar, ta ce ta yi magana ne game da hakkin gay na ba da " bege " ga wasu.
Ya kuma ce kasancewa iyaye ya sa ya kasa damuwa da lashe gasar Olympics.
Kirsty Young, wadda ta daɗe tana yin wannan taron, tana shan izinin yin aiki na wata biyu don rashin lafiya.
Da yake nuna cewa shi ne wanda aka yi watsi da shi a shirin farko na Laverne, Daley ya ce ya ji "ƙananan" fiye da dukan waɗanda ya girma tare da su domin "ba abin da ya dace a zamantakewa ba ne a so maza da mata".
Ta ce: "Har wa yau, irin wannan rashin tausayi da kuma bambancin ra'ayi sun zama ainihin abin da ya ba ni ƙarfi da kuma ƙarfin yin nasara".
Ta ce tana son ta tabbatar da cewa ita "wani abu ne", don kada ta ɓata wa kowa rai sa'ad da suka san game da batun jima'i.
Wannan masanin gwagwarmayar tagulla ta biyu ta Olympics ya zama sanannen mai ba da shawara ga LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da wasan da ya yi a wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Ostiraliya don ya jawo hankalin ƙasashe da yawa don kada su nuna bambanci ga masu luwaɗi.
Ta ce tana magana ne domin tana jin cewa ta yi farin ciki da ta yi rayuwa a buɗe ba tare da wani sakamako ba kuma tana son ta ba da " bege " ga wasu.
Wannan ɗan wasan da ya lashe gasar cin kofin duniya sau uku ya ce ya yi sha'awar wani mutum - mai shirya fina-finai na Amirka Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekara ta 2013 - "ya ba ni mamaki".
Daley ta auri Oscar mai shekara 20 da haihuwa a shekarar da ta gabata, kuma ta ce bambancin shekaru ba matsala ba ce.
"Idan kana fuskantar matsaloli da yawa a matashi sosai" - ta halarci gasar Olympics ta farko a shekara ta 14 kuma mahaifinta ya rasu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka - ta ce yana da wuya a sami wani da ya yi shekaru da ita da ya yi irin wannan rashin jin daɗi.
A watan Yuni, ma'auratan sun haifi ɗa, Robert Ray Black-Daley, kuma Daley ya ce "dukan ra'ayinsa" ya canja.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, duk game da 'ya kamata in lashe zinariya,'" ya ce.
"Ka sani, akwai wani abu mafi girma fiye da cin kofin zinariya na Olympics.
"Lambar zinare ta Olympics ita ce Robbie".
Ɗansa yana da sunan mahaifinsa Robert, wanda ya mutu a shekara ta 2011 yana da shekaru 40 bayan an gano shi da ciwon daji na kwakwalwa.
Daley ya ce mahaifinsa bai yarda cewa zai mutu ba, kuma daya daga cikin abubuwan da ya yi tambaya na karshe shi ne ko sun samu tikitin zuwa gasar Olympics ta London 2012 - domin yana son zama a jere na gaba.
"Ba zan iya gaya masa ba 'Ba za ku zauna a jere a gaban mahaifina ba,'" in ji ta.
"Na riƙe hannunsa sa'ad da ya daina numfashi kuma har yanzu bai daina numfashi ba har sai da ya mutu, a ƙarshe na yarda cewa ba a iya cin nasara a kansa ba", in ji ta.
A shekara ta gaba Daley ya yi gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ya lashe tagulla.
Ta ce: "Na san cewa abin da na yi mafarki na yi a dukan rayuwata shi ne yin iyo a gaban taron mutane a wasannin Olympics, babu abin da ya fi hakan".
Wannan kuma ya sa ta zaɓi waƙar ta farko - Proud by Heather Small - wadda ta haɗa ta da ita a shirye-shiryen Olympics kuma har yanzu tana sa ta yi rawar jiki.
