Trump yana yin tambayoyi a kai a kai a lokacin da ya bar fadar White House ko kuma yana halartar taron jama'a ko taron manema labarai da manyan jami'an da ke ziyarar.
Ba a yawan yin taron manema labarai a kai a kai.
