Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami sun afkawa Indonesia
Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka yi wa birnin Palu, Indonesia, a ranar Juma'a, sun kashe mutane 384, jami'an sun ce, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai ƙaru.
Rashin sadarwa ya sa jami'an da ke ba da taimako suka sami wahalar samun bayanai daga gundumar Donggala, wani yanki da ke arewacin garin Palu wanda ke kusa da cibiyar girgizar ƙasa da ta yi tasiri da ƙarfin 7.5 na Richter.
A Palu, bayan bala'in, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000.
Ga wasu manyan bayanai game da birnin Palu da Donggala, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu ita ce babban birnin lardin Sulawesi ta Tsakiya, wanda ke kan iyakar bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da kimanin mutane 379,800 a shekara ta 2017.
Sa'ad da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da haihuwa.
Donggala, a wani lokaci, gundumar da ke da fadin kilomita 300 (180 mil) daga gabar tekun da ke arewa maso yammacin Sulawesi.
Wannan gundumar, wanda ke karkashin yankin gudanarwa, an kiyasta yawan mutane 299,200 a shekarar 2017.
Babban tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta Kudu shine neman kifi da kuma daidaita shuka, musamman a bakin tekun Donggala.
Duk da haka, ana samun muhimmancin yin hakar nickel a wannan lardin, ko da yake yawancin su suna cikin Morowali, a gabashin Sulawesi.
A cikin shekaru 100 da suka gabata, Palu da Donggala sun sha wahala daga tsunami sau da yawa, bisa ga bayanan Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta Indonesia.
A shekara ta 1938, mutane fiye da 200 suka mutu a tsunami kuma ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala sun yi taɓarɓarewa.
A shekara ta 1996, mutane tara sun mutu a tsunami a yammacin Donggala.
A gefen duniya, Indonesia tana cikin Pacific Ring of Fire kuma saboda haka za a yi girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Waɗannan su ne manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da suka auku a cikin 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: Ranar 26 ga watan Disamba, Indonesia ta yi girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani, musamman a gabar yamma ta lardin Aceh, a arewacin Sumatra, wanda ya jawo tsunami a ƙasashe 14, har ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar Tekun Indiya, kuma fiye da rabin mutuwar sun kasance a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa ta afka wa yammacin Sumatra.
A tsibirin Nias, a gabar tekun Sumatra, an kashe ɗaruruwan mutane.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai karfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudu da tsibirin Java, wanda shi ne tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a Indonesia, kuma ta haifar da tsunami a gabar kudu da ya yi sanadiyyar mutuwar kusan mutane 700.
A shekara ta 2009: An yi girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.6 a kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wani girgizar ƙasa mai karfin 7.5 a tsibirin Mentawai, a gabashin Sumatra, ta afka wa tsunami mai tsayi na mita 10, wanda ya halaka ƙauyuka da dama kuma ya kashe mutane 300.
2016: Jihar Pidie Jaya, Aceh, ta sha wahala daga girgizar ƙasa mai zurfi da ta haifar da lalacewa, da kuma firgici daga mutanen da suka tuna da lalacewar da ta faru a cikin girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a shekarar 2004.
Ko da yake wannan ba tsunami ba ne, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu a sakamakon rushewar gine-gine.
A shekara ta 2018: Lombok, wanda ake kira tsibirin yawon bude ido, ya kuma sami babban girgizar ƙasa wanda ya kashe mutane fiye da 500, mafi yawansu a arewacin tsibirin.
Wannan girgizar ta rushe dubban gine-gine kuma ta kai dubban masu yawon bude ido.
An Kama Ɗan Sara Palin Da Laifin Yin Rikicin Cikin Gida
Track Palin, ɗan fari na Sarah Palin, tsohon gwamnan Alaska da kuma dan takarar mataimakin shugaban kasa, an kama shi da zargin kai hari.
