Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya suna neman hukuncin kisa wanda ba a saba gani ba ga wadanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York.
Masu gabatar da kara a jihar New York na neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullo Saipov, wanda ake zargi da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York, inda aka kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin kisa ne da ba a taba yi a jihohi ba tun shekarar 1953 don aikata laifuka na tarayya.
An yi zargin cewa Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya kai hari ta hanyar tura motar da ya haya daga gidan ajiyar kayayyaki zuwa ga masu tafiya da kuma masu hawa keke a kan titin keke a kan titin West Side Highway a Lower Manhattan, a watan Oktoba.
Domin a tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su bayar da hujja cewa Saipov "da gangan" ya kashe wadanda takwas kuma "da gangan" ya haifar da mummunan rauni, bisa ga wata sanarwa ta soyayya don yanke hukuncin kisa, wanda aka gabatar zuwa Kudancin Gundumar New York.
Bisa ga takardun kotu, waɗannan tuhuma biyu suna ba da damar yin hukuncin kisa.
Bayan 'yan makonni bayan harin, kotun tarayya ta yanke hukuncin kisa kan Saipov da tuhuma 22, ciki har da tuhuma takwas na kisan kai a kan yin amfani da kayan zamba, wanda masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da shi a lokuta na aikata laifuka, da kuma tuhuma na aikata mugunta da kuma ƙoƙarin lalata motocin mota.
Mai gabatar da kara ya ce harin ya bukaci "shirye-shiryen da ya dace da farko da kuma tsai da shawara", a matsayin kwatancin laifin da Saipov ya yi da "rashin hankali, rashin tausayi, da rashin hankali".
A cikin sanarwar da ta bayar, "Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi rauni, ya yi hadari, kuma ya rasa danginsa da abokansa Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlij, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza, da Alejandro Damian Pagnucco.
Mutum biyar da suka mutu a wannan hatsarin 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekara goma kenan da gundumar ta Kudu ta yanke hukuncin kisa a karo na karshe.
A watan Satumba na shekara ta 2009, an yanke wa Khalid Barnes hukuncin daurin rai a gidan yari bisa zarginsa da kashe masu sayar da miyagun ƙwayoyi biyu.
A shekarar 1953, an yi kisa na ƙarshe a kotun tarayya ta New York a kan Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka yanke hukuncin kisa a kan su da suka yi wa Soviet Union leƙen asiri a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka shige.
An kashe ma'aurata a cikin kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
A cewar takardun kotu, Saipov, dan kasar Uzbekistan, bai nuna nadamarsa ba a tsawon kwanaki da watanni bayan harin.
Da aka tambaye shi, sai ya ce yana farin ciki da abin da ya yi, in ji 'yan sanda.
Saipov ya kuma bayyana wa hukumomi cewa harin da ya kai ya yi wahayi ne ga bidiyon da ISIS ta kalli daga wayarsa, kamar yadda ake tuhumar.
Ya kuma bukaci a saka tutar kungiyar IS a dakinsa a asibiti, in ji 'yan sanda.
Ya ce bai yi laifi ba a kan zargin da aka yi masa guda 22.
David Patton, ɗaya daga cikin masu ba da shawara ga jama'a a tarayya da ke wakiltar Saipov, ya ce "yana da matukar damuwa" game da hukuncin da mai gabatar da kara ya yanke.
"A ganinsu, hukuncin kisa maimakon karɓar ɗaurin rai a kurkuku ba tare da tabbacin 'yanci ba zai ƙara wa waɗanda suka yi abin baƙin ciki ba", in ji Patton.
A baya, ƙungiyar masu kare Saipov ta roƙi mai gabatar da kara kada ya yanke hukuncin kisa.
